data.description: Introducing the epitome of modern, this is a updated modern townhouse with three bedrooms and two and a half baths. This townhouse has a spacious open floor plan, boasting high ceilings and large windows that bathe the living area in natural light. The fully renovated kitchen offers stainless steel appliances, elegant cabinetry, and quartz countertops. The master bedroom has its attached bath with modern fixtures and tasteful finishes. Additionally, the townhouse offers a balcony to unwind on after a long day. With its prime location and contemporary charm, this updated modern townhouse is an opportunity not to be missed.
